> inventory
You are empty-handed. You are wearing your socks, your boxers, your 
undershirt, your sneakers and your khakis.

> examine sneakers
Your old and beloved black Converse sneakers, a bit worn out.

> DBG_CLOTHES sneakers
'sneakers' VALUES: | feetcover: 4 | 
WORN: Yes (by hero)

> examine socks
A pair of plain white socks turned nicotine yellow in the course of time.
The right sock has a hole big enough for your toe to pop out.

> DBG_CLOTHES socks
'socks' VALUES: | feetcover: 2 | 
WORN: Yes (by hero)

> examine boxers
Just your boxer shorts (the loose type), white and plain.

> DBG_CLOTHES boxers
'boxers' VALUES: | botcover: 2 | 
WORN: Yes (by hero)

> examine undershirt
A plain white T-shaped undershirt, a few stains here and there.

> DBG_CLOTHES undershirt
'undershirt' VALUES: | topcover: 2 | 
WORN: Yes (by hero)

